Various guided reflection opportunities regarding reflection during the planning of studies, reflection as a cooperative researcher, reflection of individual learning experience and reflection of individual guided study experience.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to understand and give sense to the essence and meaning of reflection by practicing individual reflection as a member of community of reflective practitioners during the planning of student`s own studies in the context of education.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the course, the student: - plans, evaluates, and reflects upon his/her learning activities; - reflects upon his/her cooperative activities (also in the research context); - is ready to support colleagues in his/her organization.
